Below are the comments we received regarding the impact page:
In the title, please use: “ESDU: Exploring Solutions, Defining Uncertainties – 25 Years of Sustainable Community Development.”
Put “See the Journey" before "Explore Impact.”
Include animation, pop-ups, and more pictures throughout the presentation.
Use the “Arab Keepers of the Land” visual as a background image.
Add the ESDU logo.
Under Regions, please cover the entire MENA region including the Gulf and the Mediterranean.
Update KPIs
Remove elements related to AUB, and instead emphasize our keywords (critical mass, cross-cutting initiatives, etc.).
Under Cross-Cutting Initiatives, please remove “Talent.”
In the ESDU at Work section, add the five strategic objectives we discussed in the new strategy.
For KPIs, instead of focusing on “farmers,” please use “developmental actors”, and also add a KPI related to women.
Under Geographical Outreach, include: Urban Agriculture, Karianet, EvalMENA, From Seed to Table.
In Partners and Donors, add IDRC (as the creator), and include RUAF, ENI CBC, European Commission, and other UN agencies.
At the end, please have an “All-in-One: Our Ecosystem” category summarizing everything.
Add in the Core Values section: "Embedding development into relief" and "people at the center", "AI at the service of heritage"
Add a strategy section